      • openFilesystems

        protected static Map<URI,WeakReference<BundleFileSystem>> openFilesystems
        The list of open file systems. This is static so that it is shared across eventual multiple instances of this provider (such as when running in an OSGi environment). Access to this map should be synchronized to avoid opening a file system that is not in the map.
